item.title: A Note from Whistler SAI
item.description: Interjection The Whistler SAI wanted me to post this on her behalf. So I am. Hi everyone! “Hi everyone! I’m sorry I haven’t really been saying anything… I can’t seem to connect to the internet anymore. But it’s okay! There’s a friend coming by every now and again helping me out, so I’ve been giving them what I would have posted on the internet anyway! I hope you’re all doing okay… Maybe more people are reading my things now!
